{"tid":1673240,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"區選簡介會遇示威腰斬 選管會強烈譴責","createTime":"2019-10-24T14:06:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-24T14:06:52.000Z","uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e934981bd481a4afc47a9a6d9785a9a81c942354","tid":1673240,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T14:06:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/420361564693683/posts/2671862056210278/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F420361564693683%2Fposts%2F2671862056210278%2F&d=wRNUG5%2F8jzvhtT%2FDMFjpNj632Ab34%2FJQlYP9Mjrnz38%3D&h=84302310\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/420361564693683/posts/2671862056210278/</a><br />\n<br />\n【區選簡介會遇示威要腰斬 選管會強烈譴責】<br />\n<br />\n選舉管理委員會今晚（10月24日）在亞洲國際博覽館，為2019年區議會候選人及其代理人舉辦簡介會，期間接連有人示威，提出五大訴求及反對政治篩選，最終主持人稱因場內秩序關係，宣布簡介會終止，選管會對該些人士的行為表示極度遺憾，予以強烈譴責。<br />\n <br />\n選管會表示，簡介會的目的是向候選人介紹選舉活動指引內的重要環節，確保選舉在公開、公平和誠實的情況下進行。然而，有人在簡介會進行期間擾亂秩序、大聲叫嚷、向講者投擲物品，嚴重影響會場秩序，最終簡介會須取消。<br />\n <br />\n選管會又稱向來尊重表達意見的自由，但參加簡介會的人士必須遵守簡介會的場地規則，不能騷擾其他在場人士和妨礙簡介會的進行。<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n全文︰<a href=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/10-24-2019/57003\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Farticle%2F10-24-2019%2F57003&d=wRNUG5%2F8jzvhtT%2FDMFjpNj632Ab34%2FJQlYP9Mjrnz38%3D&h=2ab38935\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/10-24-2019/57003</a><br />\n<br />\n#區議會選舉<br />\n<br />\n請支持PassionPrime：<br />\n<a href=\"http://passiontimes.hk/prime/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpassiontimes.hk%2Fprime%2F&d=wRNUG5%2F8jzvhtT%2FDMFjpNj632Ab34%2FJQlYP9Mjrnz38%3D&h=e5bf4a8d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://passiontimes.hk/prime/</a><br />\n<br />\n請支持熱血時報印刷版︰<br />\n<a href=\"http://passiontimes.hk/4.0/regform.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpassiontimes.hk%2F4.0%2Fregform.php&d=wRNUG5%2F8jzvhtT%2FDMFjpNj632Ab34%2FJQlYP9Mjrn